The '''Eolgen Racovițeni Wind Farm''' is an under construction wind power project in [[Buzău County]], [[Romania]]. It will have 45 individual [[wind turbine]]s<ref>[http://www.tmctv.ro/articol_49422/o_firma_spaniola_construie__te_un_parc_de_generatoare_eoliene_in_comuna_buzoiana_racovi__eni.html O firma spaniola construieste un parc eolian in comuna buzoiana Racoviţeni {{ro}}]</ref> with a nominal output of around 1 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] which will deliver up to 45 [[Megawatt|MW]] of power, enough to power over 17,820 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately US$105 million.

